### `@Generated` annotation example:

```java
@Generated(
    value = {
        &quot;https://www.jooq.org&quot;,
        &quot;jOOQ version:3.19.0-SNAPSHOT&quot;
    },
    comments = &quot;This class is generated by jOOQ&quot;
)
```

### `Constants` content:

```java$
public final class Constants {
    // ...

    public static final String VERSION        = &quot;3.19.0-SNAPSHOT&quot;;
}
```

